Re: typing in japanese on iphone?
by chikara » Wed 04.20.2011 9:27 pm TheEnglishKnitter wrote:..... romaji with the 'microns' .....TheEnglishKnitter wrote:.... What's wrong with 'macron'? .....Nothing's wrong with macron but micron, short for micrometre, is something that wool (off the sheep's back, don't know about knitting wool) is measured in. Don't complain to me that people kick you when you're down. It's your own fault for lying there
